# EventType: 1111440000
# Descriptor: [B0 -> Jpsi [ -> mu+ mu-] K*0 [ -> K+ pi-] ]cc
# NickName: Bd_J/psiK*0_mu+mu-K+_pi-
# Documentation: Study of CKM with TDCPV analysis
# Tested: Yes
# Physics WG: TDCPV
# Responsible: Kenkichi Miyabayashi, Miho Fujii
# Email: miyabaya@cc.nara-wu.ac.jp
# Cuts: None
